Saturday Nights LIVE Radio/Club Remix DJ 
--- LIVE on Power 90.1fm Tampa Bay, it's Debacle Radio! Hosted by Chris and Derek! 

Debacle Radio is a radio show concept heard Saturday nights from 10pm - 12am and 2am - 4am Sunday Morning(EST) on WYPW POWER 90.1 FM, Tampa / Brandon, Florida. Listen Live in Tampa Florida on Power 90.1fm or Live from anywhere by downloading the FREE Power90.1 App or by streaming Live on power901.com !! We're on Spotify, iTunes Podcast, Google Play Music, Tune In, iHeart Radio, Slacker Radio, and more! Just google, Debacle Radio!

Debacle Radio, based in Tampa Bay Florida and is hosted by Derek Ammon & Chris Kiser. The show is produced by Gabriel Paaga (Samoa Good Music)& Dez Middleton (The Rave Gang). Debacle Radio focuses on a broad range of cutting edge electronic dance genres as well as EDM club hits and remixes. The show features exclusive guest mixes, new weekly releases, interviews, the Debacle Radio's Top 5 Countdown as well as featuring a “LIT Track of the Week”, Throwback Track and the Samoa Good Music’s “Good people, Good Vibe track of the Week”.

This show is not your typical radio show! #TuneIn

