I lead creative and brand teams, including talented brand strategists, creatives, UX/D, content strategists, and program/project managers.

For the past two+ decades, I've built and managed successful creative brand marketing and communications platforms for many established companies. However, more importantly, guiding teams of driven, thoughtful individuals, I've helped foster meaningful dialogue and engagement around shared passions: one story, one message, one conversation at a time.

My professional sweet spot is when creativity, messaging, and data come together to tell an exciting, enduring story that connects with customers and stakeholders, and then doing that at scale. 

I've conceptualized, launched, produced, and managed corporate, employer, and product brands and communications platforms for technology companies, consumer brands, as well as for private organizations and universities – while managing and protecting the brands to ensure that the message, identity, domains, and positioning remains authentic and singular.

My specialties include:

Creative and strategic leadership; Brand portfolio strategy and management, including measurement and insights;  Brand reputation, protection, and domains; Creative brand positioning and visual system development and management; Creative strategy, messaging, and campaigns, including product and event brands; Digital and social media; content development and distribution; media and partnerships; and;

Saying it in a way you haven't heard before;

Building teams with vision, purpose, cohesion, and empathy

A 4-wood off the fairway or an 8-iron from 160 yards;

Puns;

Forging lasting connections around the world.

